are-getting-wrong-about-israel-according-to-nathan-thrall/0000018e-3756-d606-a5ff-7ff7ffb10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方为斋月的第一个周五祈祷做准备，哈马斯呼吁“保护阿克萨”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-prepare-for-ramadans-first-friday-prayers-as-hamas-calls-to-protect-al-aqsa/0000018e-3e2c-d9ae-ad9f-3fec64880000</link><description>为了保持假期第一周的相对平静，以色列警方计划允许 5 万名信徒自由出入，这些信徒预计将抵达阿克萨清真寺大院参加本月的第一个周五祈祷。斋月</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 19:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-prepare-for-ramadans-first-friday-prayers-as-hamas-calls-to-protect-al-aqsa/0000018e-3e2c-d9ae-ad9f-3fec64880000</guid></item><item><title>即使是反对以色列加沙战争的犹太人也无法逃脱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/even-jews-who-oppose-israels-war-in-gaza-cant-escape-it/0000018e-3d9e-d5c2-a5ff-bffe30400000</link><description>乔纳森·格雷泽的奥斯卡获奖电影《感兴趣的区域》与以色列和巴勒斯坦人无关。但如今，每个犹太人都应该表达他们对以色列和加沙的看法</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:34:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/even-jews-who-oppose-israels-war-in-gaza-cant-escape-it/0000018e-3d9e-d5c2-a5ff-bffe30400000</guid></item><item><title>汗尤尼斯在废墟中：卫星图像显示加沙第二大城市大面积遭到破坏，建筑物被夷为平地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/khan-yunis-in-rubble-sat-images-reveal-mass-destruction-in-gazas-second-largest-city/0000018e-3d30-d670-a5be-fd3e9a650000</link><description>尽管以色列军队有所撤退，但加沙地带仍然发生严重战斗。这些图像显示过去几周汗尤尼斯遭受的巨大破坏</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 17:29:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/khan-yunis-in-rubble-sat-images-reveal-mass-destruction-in-gazas-second-largest-city/0000018e-3d30-d670-a5be-fd3e9a650000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 160 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-0