3-14/ty-article/.premium/pa-president-abbas-to-ask-mohammad-mustafa-to-form-new-palestinian-government/0000018e-3cac-d30d-a7de-7cbf89b70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙卡塔尔建造的豪华社区遭遇激烈战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-meets-fierce-fighting-in-gazas-qatari-built-luxury-neighborhood/0000018e-3c37-d21d-a3ef-3f7786a70000</link><description>以色列军队指挥官表示，汗尤尼斯的哈马德社区的部分地区似乎是为以色列国防军部队进入该地区的那一天做准备的，其中一些建筑战略性地容纳了专为城市战斗而设计的资产</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-meets-fierce-fighting-in-gazas-qatari-built-luxury-neighborhood/0000018e-3c37-d21d-a3ef-3f7786a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方支持枪杀 12 岁巴勒斯坦儿童的警官。他的父亲坚称他从未危及过他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/family-of-palestinian-boy-shot-dead-by-police-in-east-jerusalem-say-he-posed-no-danger/0000018e-390b-dc74-adbe-bdaf41ef0000</link><description>12 岁拉米·哈姆丹 (Rami Hamdan) 的父亲亲眼目睹儿子在东耶路撒冷难民营被枪杀，坚称自己从未将烟花指向警察部队。司法部官员估计这名警察不会被起诉，因为高级警官私下警告称，这一事件可能导致东耶路撒冷局势升级</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 04:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/family-of-palestinian-boy-shot-dead-by-police-in-east-jerusalem-say-he-posed-no-danger/0000018e-390b-dc74-adbe-bdaf41ef0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的分配困境：随着饥饿蔓延，捐助者寻求私营公司来处理援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-distribution-dilemma-as-hunger-spreads-donors-seek-private-firms-to-handle-aid/0000018e-39fd-d3fc-adff-b9ff1f180000</link><description>第一批海上援助物资——200吨食品和药品——已离开塞浦路斯前往加沙地带，但后勤困难将使这一过程变得复杂，美国政府没有解决方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 04:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-distribution-dilemma-as-hunger-spreads-donors-seek-private-firms-to-handle-aid/0000018e-39fd-d3fc-adff-b9ff1f180000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡称哈马斯的提议“不切实际”，称战时内阁将于周五召开会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article-live/report-u-s-would-back-israeli-op-against-hamas-leaders-in-rafah-if-idf-does-not-invade/0000018e-3aad-d823-adaf-7baf11d50000</link><description>哈马斯表示已向调解人提出了全面的停战协议愿景 ■ 人质家属暂时封锁特拉维夫高速公路 ■ 巴勒斯坦权力机构主席马哈茂德·阿巴斯责成穆罕默德·穆斯塔法组建新的巴勒斯坦政府 ■ 以色列国防军称，三枚火箭弹袭击了以色列北部的基布兹 ■ 袭击者刺伤事件中一名来自加沙的 22 岁以色列公民 ■ 美国参议院多数党领袖呼吁以色列举行新选举 ■ 美国制裁约旦河西岸的两个前哨基地、三名定居者</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article-live/report-u-s-would-back-israeli-op-against-hamas-leaders-in-rafah-if-idf-does-not-invade/0000018e-3aad-d823-adaf-7baf11d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将废除“多余”的情报部，略微精简臃肿的政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-scrap-superfluous-intelligence-ministry-slightly-slimming-bloated-government/0000018e-3999-d2fd-a1fe-3df9ac7a0000</link><description>现任部长吉拉·加姆利尔(Gila Gamliel)将接任科学部长，接替奥菲尔·阿库尼斯(Ofir Akunis)，奥菲尔·阿库尼斯将前往纽约担任以色列总领事</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:16:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-scrap-superfluous-intelligence-ministry-slightly-slimming-bloated-government/0000018e-3999-d2fd-a1fe-3df9ac7a0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学100名教职员工抗议解雇指控以色列加沙种族灭绝的学者，怀疑哈马斯暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/100-hebrew-university-faculty-protest-suspension-of-scholar-alleging-israeli-gaza-genocide/0000018e-3993-d3fc-adff-b9b383330000</link><description>现任和前任教职员工写道，尽管他们反对沙尔赫布-凯沃尔基安的观点，但管理层无权让她停职。他们补充说，此举可能会增加国际学术抵制该大学的呼声</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/100-hebrew-university-faculty-protest-suspension-of-scholar-alleging-israeli-gaza-genocide/0000018e-3993-d3fc-adff-b9b383330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学是否应该解雇一名称哈马斯暴行是“谎言”的学者？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-13/ty-article/.highlight/should-an-israeli-university-fire-an-academic-who-said-hamas-atrocities-are-lies/0000018e-38e7-d21d-a3ef-3be7aa4f0000</link><description>在这一点上，如果所有这些受惊的大学管理部门和愤怒的抵制者都得逞，校园里唯一剩下的争论将是关于自助餐厅的选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:13:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-13/ty-article/.highlight/should-an-israeli-university-fire-an-academic-who-said-hamas-atrocities-are-lies/0000018e-38e7-d21d-a3ef-3be7aa4f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>